{
  "stem": "1895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 373.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Most of them had the iron cross decorations on them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was eerie, you know, even for those days, to see people get off a train, which was like private Pullman cars, brought in in-- in excellent condition.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "People get off this train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Some of them were in wheelchairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And some of them had the crosses hanging down on their chest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And I saw them all-- some of them went in the Red Cross cars.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Some of them went-- walked in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Some of them were pushed in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Everything went in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I need to live many years to be able to describe what I saw on that ramp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was in Auschwitz-- I lived through-- by the way, I lived through the revolt in Auschwitz, which happened on September 7th.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was in very close proximity to the crematorium number 3 and 4 when they blew the-- when-- when the revolt occurred.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, the guards that were with us made us lay down, and we had to bury our head in the ground until the whole thing was over, so I-- I didn't actually see.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So when we got up, we saw a few SS guards were laying dead on the ground near the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The revolt was over for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We had some anxious days later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They threatened to kill a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then we had a series of hangings after that, where almost every Sunday they would take out dozens of people, you know, and line them up and hang them in view-- full view of everybody.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
